Package: TreeHeatmap
Type: Package
Title: A package to plot heatmaps at different levels of a tree
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ruizhu Huang
Maintainer: Ruizhu Huang <ruizhuRH@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows users to align heatmaps to nodes of a tree. 
    It also provides annotation functions that have similar syntax to ggplot2 
    to annotate rows or columns of the heatmap.
Dependends:
    R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    ggtree,
    ape,
    dplyr,
    data.table,
    rlang,
    methods,
    ggnewscale,
    ggdendro
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    BiocStyle,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
